name: victory
description: This example shows how to load data from a CSV file using React hooks and visualize the result using [Victory Charts](https://formidable.com/open-source/victory/). Inspired by this [Victory example from Swizec Teller](https://codesandbox.io/s/3v3q013x36?from-embed) in [React for Data Visualization](https://reactfordataviz.com/).
